  "merge_notes": "School conflict: 2 ICT vs 1 Market Structure; picked ICT by majority. The Foundation project defines BOS purely as close beyond swing point without requiring displacement or sweep, while ICT projects require sweep + displacement. Unified card includes both perspectives but prioritizes ICT's displacement requirement. Also, The Foundation emphasizes waiting for reverse swing point after BOS, which is added.",
